variable muet NUTD 'number of the descriptor array TD' entier ; 
variable NUTYEF 'type number of Finite Elements'  entier ;  
variable NBELFI 'number of finite elements'       entier ;   
variable NDIMES 'dimension of the euclidean space 2 or 3' entier ; 
variable NBJECA 'data number of stress'           entier ;       
variable NBPIEF 'computation point number of stress on a FE' entier ;
